@startuml
title 图3-2 系统数据流与控制流示意图

top to bottom direction
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangleStyle plain
skinparam roundcorner 0

rectangle "环境数据\n温湿度 / 光照 / 土壤湿度" as Data
rectangle "STM32控制节点" as STM32
rectangle "树莓派边缘网关" as Pi
rectangle "本地数据库\nSQLite" as DB
rectangle "Web界面" as Web
rectangle "云平台\nMQTT" as Cloud
rectangle "执行模块\n水泵 / 灯带 / OLED" as Actuator
actor "用户" as User

Data --> STM32
STM32 --> Pi
Pi --> DB
Pi --> Web
Pi --> Cloud

User ..> Web
Web ..> Pi
Pi ..> STM32
STM32 ..> Actuator

legend right
实线：数据流
虚线：控制流
endlegend

@enduml